Ms. Reid, do you believe
Danny was ever sexually abused?

47:31.185 --> 47:32.186
No.

47:33.687 --> 47:36.690
- I'm sorry. Let me ask that again.
- I don't believe he was abused.

47:38.609 --> 47:43.238
Ms. Reid, I understand
that this is very difficult for you.

47:43.822 --> 47:46.158
I just want to remind you
that you are under oath.

47:48.035 --> 47:50.662
Are you sure
there wasn't any kind of abuse?

47:50.662 --> 47:51.747
Objection.

47:51.747 --> 47:53.165
Are you sure you didn't hear anything?

47:53.165 --> 47:54.291
Asked and answered.

47:54.291 --> 47:56.502
- Are you sure that you didn't see any--
- Sustained.

48:03.175 --> 48:04.176
Ms. Reid?

48:05.385 --> 48:06.386
No.

48:09.932 --> 48:10.933
No further questions.

48:11.850 --> 48:12.851
Ms. Richards.

48:14.269 --> 48:15.437
No questions, Your Honor.

48:15.437 --> 48:17.314
The witness is excused.

48:32.579 --> 48:34.706
We'll adjourn till tomorrow.

48:34.706 --> 48:36.166
Escort the jury out please.

48:38.085 --> 48:39.086
All rise.

48:47.302 --> 48:48.554
Danny, stand up.

